00:17:30.620 --> 00:17:31.850 align:middle line:90%
Work.

00:17:31.850 --> 00:17:33.865 align:middle line:84%
There's no way to find
that proper balance.

00:17:33.865 --> 00:17:34.760 align:middle line:90%
>>I avoid social situations.

00:17:34.760 --> 00:17:36.340 align:middle line:84%
>>I'm so uncomfortable
with the way I look.

00:17:36.340 --> 00:17:37.660 align:middle line:90%
I don't want people to see me.

00:17:37.660 --> 00:17:39.600 align:middle line:84%
>>I know people my age
