00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:40.880 align:middle line:90%
I might overdose.

00:17:40.880 --> 00:17:42.800 align:middle line:90%
There's got to be another way.

00:17:42.800 --> 00:17:44.674 align:middle line:84%
>>Sometimes, I wish
life was just easier.

00:17:44.674 --> 00:17:46.590 align:middle line:84%
>>I don't know what I
