00:17:52.456 --> 00:17:52.792 align:middle line:90%
>>I feel nauseous all the time.

00:17:52.792 --> 00:17:54.620 align:middle line:90%
>>And my thoughts race.

00:17:54.620 --> 00:17:55.370 align:middle line:90%
>>Racing thoughts.

00:17:55.370 --> 00:17:56.312 align:middle line:10%
>>So overwhelming.

00:17:56.312 --> 00:17:58.145 align:middle line:10%
Sometimes I just feel
