00:18:54.800 --> 00:18:58.350 align:middle line:84%
drug therapies, psychotherapy,
and a history of all

00:18:58.350 --> 00:19:02.810 align:middle line:84%
the medications that have
been given to the patient.

00:19:02.810 --> 00:19:05.540 align:middle line:84%
>>And I'll also pay a
