00:19:08.470 --> 00:19:10.650 align:middle line:84%
gives me a lot of
information about how

00:19:10.650 --> 00:19:13.370 align:middle line:90%
they interact socially.

00:19:13.370 --> 00:19:18.530 align:middle line:84%
>>Then, of critical importance
to me is the family history.

00:19:18.530 --> 00:19:21.600 align:middle line:84%
And of course, you look at the
