disease oftentimes

00:20:08.610 --> 00:20:12.210 align:middle line:84%
is manifested as a
depressed patient.

00:20:12.210 --> 00:20:15.220 align:middle line:84%
Cardiac disease
may manifest itself

00:20:15.220 --> 00:20:18.250 align:middle line:84%
with palpitations and
symptoms very similar

00:20:18.250 --> 00:20:20.160 align:middle line:90%
to an anxiety attack.

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:25.090 align:middle line:84%
Many medical conditions are
accompanied by depression.

00:20:25.090 --> 00:20:28.510 align:middle line:10%
>>When we put all of
these parts together,

00:20:28.510 --> 00:20:33.350 align:middle line:10%
we get the biopsychosocial
picture of that patient.

00:20:33.350 --> 00:20:36.240 align:middle line:10%
>>Finally, the
psychiatrist will match up

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:38.480 align:middle line:10%
this picture with one
of the symptom clusters

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:41.550 align:middle line:10%
that's described in the
"Diagnostics and Statistics

00:20:41.550 --> 00:20:43.870 align:middle line:10%
Manual," which
lists all currently

00:20:43.870 --> 00:20:47.000 align:middle line:10%
recognized mental
health disorders.

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:48.645 align:middle line:10%
While it's very
rare for a person

00:20:48.645 --> 00:20:51.780 align:middle line:10%
to fit every single
diagnostic criteria,

00:20:51.780 --> 00:20:55.270 align:middle line:10%
the DSM-IV is the
most widely used tool

00:20:55.270 --> 00:20:57.175 align:middle line:10%
in diagnosing mental
health disorders.

00:20:57.175 --> 00:21:01.250 align:middle line:90%


00:21:01.250 --> 00:21:03.670 align:middle line:84%
>>We're trying to
accurately pinpoint

00:21:03.670 --> 00:21:06.790 align:middle line:84%
what are some of the biological
factors that are contributing

00:21:06.790 --> 00:21:08.800 align:middle line:90%
to their current picture.

00:21:08.800 --> 00:21:10.880 align:middle line:84%
What are some of their
psychological issues that

00:21:10.880 --> 00:21:13.496 align:middle line:84%
are also impacting
their emotional health?

00:21:13.496 --> 00:21:15.900 align:middle line:84%
And then finally, what are
some of the social issues

00:21:15.900 --> 00:21:17.977 align:middle line:84%
and relationship
