00:21:17.977 --> 00:21:20.435 align:middle line:84%
a contribution to the way that
they're feeling emotionally?

00:21:20.435 --> 00:21:46.350 align:middle line:90%


00:21:46.350 --> 00:21:48.910 align:middle line:84%
>>One of the most
important realizations

00:21:48.910 --> 00:21:53.160 align:middle line:84%
that came from wise
