00:22:21.990 --> 00:22:25.120 align:middle line:90%


00:22:25.120 --> 00:22:29.180 align:middle line:84%
By understanding the elements
and how they combine uniquely

00:22:29.180 --> 00:22:32.680 align:middle line:84%
in each individual,
