00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:36.483 align:middle line:84%
the energetic processes at
play in the disease process.

00:22:36.483 --> 00:22:39.201 align:middle line:90%


00:22:39.201 --> 00:22:42.400 align:middle line:10%
>>These five elements were
seen to form in human beings

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:46.430 align:middle line:10%
into three biological
