Then, it has to be metabolized.

00:23:42.350 --> 00:23:44.540 align:middle line:84%
>>It's the pitta
dosha that actually

00:23:44.540 --> 00:23:48.650 align:middle line:84%
digests food and
impressions from the world

00:23:48.650 --> 00:23:52.440 align:middle line:84%
